1- This arena can get confusing.  The room is full of switches and each
   switch swaps between 2 different mazes.  Your aim is to get to the exit
   on the right. There area couple of ways to get there.
2- Press the first switch at the top.
3- Go right and press the switch near the flame torch.                                                                             
4- Press the switch just below that one.
5- Walk up and press the switch there.  Collect the goodies and press
   the switch again.
6- Go down and press the bottom switch.
7- Walk down and press the next switch down.
8- Go right and press the switch there.
9- You can now go out the exit.

1- Go into the center of the arena and take the transporter.
2- Collect the Chain Gun and return.  You will need to use this on
   Kilmando wholooks like the other orcs, but is much stronger and smarter.
3- Destroy all the orcs.  The exit will not open until Kilmando is dead.
