 there's any money there to collect, get it. Take the right exit. Go down
 through the arch and open the door with a key. Leave via the bottom exit.

 Destroy the life stores to gain extra lives. Use an orb to free the girl
 from the prison. Take the bottom exit There is a combination switch here.
