them so that the 2 walls separating you and the transporter are gone. Take
the transporter. Step on the pressure pad and return. Go up and step on the
pressure pad to open the wall and walk down to the spikes. Go down and step
over the pressure pad twice. You will now be able to reach the bottom exit.
If you want to get the bonus items, step on the pressure pad near the exit,
